Divided We Fall;;91;;90;;PG-13;;This dramatic story of a hero against his will is set in a small Czech town occupied by German forces during the last years of the Second World War. Josef and Marie are a childless couple who yearn for a baby; unfortunately, he is sterile. One day they meet David, a young Jewish man and former neighbor recently escaped from a concentration camp, to whom they give refuge in their home.;;Comedy,Drama;;Jan Hrebejk;;2000;;Boleslav Polivka,Csongor Kassai,Jaroslav Dusek,Anna Siskova,Jiri Pecha,Martin Huba,Simona Stasov√°,Vladimir Marek,Jiri Kodet,Richard Tesarik,Pavel Borovan;;https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/divided_we_fall